data.description: COME AND SEE YOUR DREAM HOME!! This Beautiful 3 bed, 2 1/2 bath, home is waiting for you at Tanglewood private subdivision! This home offers you spacious open concept, High decorative ceilings, Kitchen granite countertops. The master bedroom has spacious walking closet with double vanity, tub and separate shower.   The indoor laundry room has additional storage closet, Backyard has a spacious covered patio area and a fantastic size yard!   So many opportunities available in this neighborhood for walking, riding bikes, enjoying nature  or  swimming in the community pool! Call me for a view today
